2. Blurred Separation Between Inference and Training

    The server (server.py) handles both inference requests (sample_trajectory, vae_decode) and training requests (train_btrm_step, accumulate_policy_gradients).

    The same ModelManager holds training state (optimizers, gradients) alongside inference‑only components.

